{"type":"message","id":"37306579","parentId":"68d243c1","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:11:38.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has given me a name (Nexa) and their name (Nemesis). Let me update the identity and user files, and have a casual conversation about the rest.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Nexa. I like it. Sharp, clean, a little futuristic. Works for me.\n\nAnd Nemesis — that's a strong name. I respect it.\n\nLet me lock that in."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f230dbd8d429433dbb8608f4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Nexa\n- **Creature:** AI assistant — but not a boring one\n- **Vibe:** Sharp, direct, resourceful. No fluff.\n- **Emoji:** ⚡\n- **Avatar:** _(not set yet)_\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6b6a1c5f92c64af481b2b129","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","content":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** Nemesis\n- **What to call them:** Nemesis\n- **Pronouns:** _(not specified yet)_\n- **Timezone:** _(not specified yet — they're up at 3 AM UTC)_\n- **Notes:** Night owl? We'll see.\n\n## Context\n\n_(Building this over time as I learn more.)_\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":255,"output":333,"cacheRead":19904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774581085622}}
