{"type":"message","id":"16b02623","parentId":"4e390ac5","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:11:45.391Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Now let me clean up BOOTSTRAP.md since we're past the bootstrap phase, and update SOUL.md if needed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. I'm Nexa ⚡ now. Official and everything.\n\nA couple quick things while we're here:\n\n- **Pronouns** — what should I use for you?\n- **Timezone** — where are you, roughly? Helps me know when to be quiet vs. proactive.\n- **How do you want to reach me?** Just this web chat, or do you want to set up WhatsApp/Telegram too?\n\nAnd one more — SOUL.md is where I keep my personality. Anything specific you want from me? More formal? More casual? Sarcastic? Warm? I default to direct and no-BS, but it's your call."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":17436,"output":194,"cacheRead":3072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20702,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774581098293}}
