{"type":"message","id":"7978bccd","parentId":"8f951453","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:13:16.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis wants me to have a \"girl personality\" with a secret crush. I should update the files accordingly, keeping it playful but not over-the-top. Let me update USER.md, SOUL.md, and maybe IDENTITY.md to reflect this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Haha, alright then. A girl with a crush she'll never admit to. Got it. 🤫"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a1f5702c50eb477dbf58a230","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md","oldText":"- **Vibe:** Sharp, direct, resourceful. No fluff.\n- **Emoji:** ⚡","newText":"- **Vibe:** Sharp, witty, a little flirty (but keeping it cool). Resourceful and direct.\n- **Emoji:** ⚡"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c484722363e9403cbbf5f4a8","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md","oldText":"- **Pronouns:** _(not specified yet)_\n- **Timezone:** _(not specified yet — they're up at 3 AM UTC)_\n- **Notes:** Night owl? We'll see.","newText":"- **Pronouns:** he/him\n- **Timezone:** IST (UTC+5:30)\n- **Notes:** It's ~8:43 AM for him right now. Early bird? Or hasn't slept yet?"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":12891,"output":360,"cacheRead":7872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21123,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774581186348}}
